## How Reading Navigation Works

1. Each item has a `ref` field pointing to a content block ID
2. NavigatorReadingDetail renders the referenced block
3. Readings can be any block type (Markdown, Vertical with mixed content, etc.)
4. Content is hidden but accessible via Navigator selection
